{"tid":1553994,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[回帶] 市民投訴黃毓民擲蕉行為過激","createTime":"2019-09-08T20:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T01:01:34.000Z","uid":56533,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e008d4d0f79b33726cef03d4f9320c364b7ed7ad","tid":1553994,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T20:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6tnj5S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6tnj5S.jpg&h=4469d7db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n30.10.2008 13:11<br />\n立法會申訴部，在月中施政報告發表後一個多星期，共接到七十多個市民，針對社民連黃毓民擲香蕉的意見，多數都表示不認同，認為粗暴、野蠻無禮和過激，亦有人認為會對社會和下一代造成負面影響，甚至是影響立法會和香港形象。有市民建議立法會警告或譴責黃毓民，或交由警方跟進，亦有一人贊成這次的激進言行。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官曾蔭權本月15日到立法會宣讀施政報告時，建議長者申請生果金要審查資產，黃毓民向曾蔭權怒擲三條香蕉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=71854&amp;csid=261_381&amp;PageSpeed=noscript\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D71854%26csid%3D261_381%26PageSpeed%3Dnoscript&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BvUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=4877320c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=71854&amp;csid=261_381&amp;PageSpeed=noscript</a><br />\n<br />\n當年投訴黃毓民擲蕉既70位市民過激, 睇到今日火燒中環站會有咩意見?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5a5c35d785c5d193d0f2acf8047aba31072d40","tid":1553994,"uid":119478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T20:16:28.000Z","msg":"爆血管"},{"pid":"2b647285998f13c8ffb66f3bdb0f2bb3aa603a36","tid":1553994,"uid":59976,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T20:17:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人欠勇武派實在太多, 邊個屌勇武邊個就係鬼</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81aa4eb70d3a86bd341aaba4ad0a759ba846c889","tid":1553994,"uid":159916,"like":8,"dislike":0